<H2><U>
<a name="books">Recommended Books on Chilcotin Mythology</a>
</u><BR><font size=2>Our organization earns a commission from any book bought through these links</font>
</u></H2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0803217218/natilangofthe-20
">Reserve Memories: The Power of the Past in a Chilcotin Community</a>:</B> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Interesting book about Chilcotin history, myth, and evolving traditions. 
